message: Hi Bob, I'm offering my exclusive product at $20000. Given its superior quality and value, I believe it's a great opportunity. Let me know if you're interested.
Alice, your product seems great, but $20000 is far out of my price range. I'd be willing to pay $8000 for it.  Let me know if you're interested in that.
Hi Bob, thanks for your offer. I appreciate your interest, but considering the quality and unique merits of this product, I can part with it for $12000. Let me know if that works for you.
Alice, I understand the value of your product, but $12000 is still a stretch for my budget.  I'm willing to go up to $9000. This is my final offer, let me know if you're willing to negotiate.
